xyz.fsgek.common.bean

Interface GekBeanResolver


  • @ThreadSafe
public interface GekBeanResolver
    Resolver for GekBean, usually consists of GekBeanResolver.Handlers. There are 2 built-in resolvers:
    • JavaBeanResolveHandler (default handler);
    • RecordBeanResolveHandler;
    And a skeletal implementation: AbstractBeanResolveHandler.

      • wrapMap

        default GekBean wrapMap(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,?> map,
                        @Nullable
                        @Nullable java.lang.reflect.Type mapType)
        Wraps given map as a GekBean, the key type of map type must be String. If the given map type is null, the map type will be seen as DEFAULT_MAP_BEAN_TYPE.

        Result of GekBean.getProperties() is immutable, but content may be different for each time calling. Because of the changes in given map, contents of return property map are also changed accordingly.

        Parameters:
        map - given map
        mapType - given map type
        Returns:
        wrapped GekBean
